 tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllCheckboxComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide all tokens to the users."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeCheckboxComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"CheckboxComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"radio button","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"checkboxes","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Radio button"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"checkboxes"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"code":"SizeSemanticToken","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"), opacities ("},{"code":"OpacitySemanticToken","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"borders (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BorderRadiusSemanticToke